    <h2 class="section-title">Restaurant range with salamander brands we service.</h2>

    <ul class="brand-list">
      <li><strong>Vulcan</strong> (ITW Food Equipment Group). VR-60 with salamander. Dominant LA install base for this premium tier. <a href="/brands/vulcan-range-repair/">Vulcan range repair brand page</a> and <a href="/brands/vulcan/">Vulcan brand hub</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Wolf Industrial</strong> (Sub-Zero Group commercial division). Challenger XL CHSC60 with integrated salamander. Distinct parts catalog from residential Wolf cooking. <a href="/brands/wolf-range-repair/">Wolf range repair brand page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Garland US-Range</strong> (Welbilt). U Series with salamander. Heavy-duty stainless construction. <a href="/brands/garland-range-repair/">Garland range repair brand page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Montague</strong> (Welbilt). Legend series with salamander. Premium tier. <a href="/brands/montague-oven-repair/">Montague oven repair brand page</a>.</li>
    </ul>
