</section>

<!-- 07 WHY US -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">07 · Why operators call us</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Eight reasons.</h2>

    <ul class="why-list">
      <li><strong>Salamander specialty.</strong> Most LA appliance shops decline salamander work; the niche fits our practitioner model.</li>
      <li><strong>Combined dispatch.</strong> Salamander plus range component repair in single visit, single $120 diagnostic, no second-visit fee.</li>
      <li><strong>Wolf Commercial vs residential disambiguation.</strong> Different parts catalogs, different authorized service networks. We verify by serial and source through the correct pipeline.</li>
      <li><strong>LA pre-fire permit awareness.</strong> We document equipment and installation context at every service call so operators have records for fire marshal inspections.</li>
      <li><strong>Common salamander parts on the van.</strong> Vulcan VR-60 salamander burner heads, igniters, thermocouples; sourced through ITW pipeline.</li>
      <li><strong>BHGS #A49573 plus EPA 608 Universal certified (#1346255700410) scope.</strong> See our <a href="/credentials/licensed/">licensing page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>$120 commercial diagnostic, no after-hours surcharge.</strong> Phones answered 24/7.</li>
      <li><strong>Same-day across LA, OC, Ventura.</strong> Premium-tier Beverly Hills, Bel Air, Hollywood, Pasadena, West Hollywood operations served from multiple branches.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Sister sub-services: <a href="/commercial/range-repair/gas-range-repair/">commercial gas range repair</a>, <a href="/commercial/range-repair/french-top-range-repair/">French top range repair</a>. Sister pillars: <a href="/commercial/oven-repair/">commercial oven repair</a>, <a href="/commercial/grill-repair/">commercial grill repair</a>, <a href="/commercial/griddle-repair/">commercial griddle repair</a>, <a href="/commercial/charbroiler-repair/">commercial charbroiler repair</a>, <a href="/commercial/exhaust-hood-repair/">commercial exhaust hood repair</a>. Parent: <a href="/commercial/range-repair/">commercial range repair pillar</a>.</p>
  </div>
